    "description": "The tool is aimed at standardizing the intensity distribution of prostate\nT2-weighted MRI by employing a deep learning\u2013based model. The model takes\nas input heterogeneous T2-weighted prostate images in DICOM format and\ngenerates the corresponding harmonized images, also in DICOM format, in\nwhich the intensity characteristics will approximate those of a curated reference domain composed of high-quality, high-contrast T2-weighted prostate scans.",
